<unittitle>The 'Homes' Herald, 1974 [Methodist Homes for Children]</unittitle>
<unitdate>December 1974</unitdate>
<abstract><span style="font-style:italic">The 'Homes' Herald</span> was a newsletter of the Methodist Homes for Children. This is a copy of the December 1974 edition. It has a picture of some young children 'helping out' by sweeping the front steps at Mofflyn. There are also photos of other children and buildings. The news items give a small amount of information about each Home and news about the staff. The newsletter also appeals for funds, explains how previous support has helped, and lets readers know what more they can do.</abstract>
</archref>
</objectXMLWrap>

